data.description: Beautiful one level home on an amazing lot in Silver Creek community. This unique home features incredible indoor and outdoor living with a great big outdoor patio area. With a private entrance for a 2 bedroom attached casita, this home has so much functionality. Wonderful open floor plan, clean, and move-in ready with great community amenities.
